#: inc/tpl/options_page.php:78
msgid "If you choose this option the Google Analytics integration will be disabled as well as all following features including \"anonymize_ip\". However, you can still use the Opt-out Shortcode. This is useful if you already have integrated another plugin and only need the Opt-out feature."
